*Drugačije* se razmišlja o tom pitanju. (One thinks differently about that question.)
Moguće je da će *drugačije* biti riješeno. (It is possible that it will be solved differently.)
Odlučili smo da se stvari rade *drugačije*. (We decided to do things differently.)
Bilo je *drugačije* nego što smo očekivali. (It was different than what we expected.)
Njegov stav je bio *drugačije*. (His attitude was different.)